                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-279-off1567 t18320906-279-cd1568"></join>, 1 coat, value 1l.; 3 pair of boots, value 20s.; 2 shawls, value 12s., and 1 pair of shoes, value 6s.
